comments.body:
This is so that i18next extensions can add / extend properties in their declaration files:

```ts
declare module 'i18next' {
    interface DetectionPluginOptions {
       a: string;
    }
}
```

`hapi` does this too for example: https://github.com/DefinitelyTyped/DefinitelyTyped/blob/14d0a6329aaf71eaa43e6d87e43e6ec74ea17c1c/types/vision/index.d.ts#L244-L268
